::Prowl::

Prowl looks from Lunarpine to Shadow Wing.

"The predacons attacked," he explains, "Shuko and his group were with them. 
Then the Alliance came in, attacked them from behind, and left. We fought 
back the rest of them, but the Ark's nearly destroyed."
